snippet.title: Sneak King for Xbox 360 Trailer
snippet.description:
Gears of War has nothing on this...

"Sneak King" is a budget title (under $5!) put out by Burger King for the Xbox 360. The game stars everyone's favorite extremely creepy ad character, "The King", as he apparently stalks people waiting for the perfect oppotunity to feed them. Possibly the creepiest game of all time.
